1. RESEARCH NOTE: See plan/001_b92a9b2b603f/architecture/firmware_wire_contract.md §Reply Disambiguation and §Field Definitions for exact byte offsets. response[0]==0x51 => typed reply. response[1] is the cmd echo byte that determines the shape. Use defensive .get() indexing — replies may be truncated.
